    "body": "I just realised that in the [`ERC-1155 Metadata URI JSON Schema`](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1155#erc-1155-metadata-uri-json-schema) section it states:\r\n\r\n> If the string `{id}` exists in any JSON value, it MUST be replaced with the actual token ID, by all client software that follows this standard.\r\n\r\nThus, that clarifies it :)",
